.SH NAME
pstr-reply-ai - Generate an AI-assisted reply


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBpstr reply ai [id] [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate a reply or reply-all draft from a configured AI template, then save or send it through the regular Postero flow.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB--account\fP=""
	account name or email to send from

.PP
\fB--all\fP[=false]
	reply to all recipients

.PP
\fB--body\fP=""
	body hint passed to the template

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for ai

.PP
\fB--instruction\fP=""
	high-level reply instruction for the template

.PP
\fB--send\fP[=false]
	send reply immediately

.PP
\fB--subject\fP=""
	subject hint passed to the template

.PP
\fB--template\fP=""
	ai template name from config

.PP
\fB--var\fP=[]
	additional template variables as key=value


